videos.description: Nebraska's James Palmer Jr. dribbles around a screen and delivers a bounce pass to Isaiah Roby for a one-handed slam.
videos.headline: Roby opens scoring with one-handed dunk

videos.description: Indiana guard Romeo Langford drives and makes a difficult floater, adding a trip to the foul line.
videos.headline: Langford sinks off-balance and-1

videos.description: James Palmer Jr. crosses up his defender and drives to the hoop for a powerful one-handed dunk before the halftime buzzer.
videos.headline: Nebraska's Palmer crosses over and rises up for big finish

videos.description: Glynn Watson Jr. hits the floor and loses the ball but gets a steal while lying on the ground.
videos.headline: Watson Jr. makes an unbelievable steal while on the floor
